Betty Schade https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Betty_Schade 0 Betty Schade (27 March 1895 – 27 March 1982) was a German-born American actress of the silent era. She appeared in about 135 films between 1913 and 1921. Betty_Schade ( 27_March_1895 – 27_March_1982 ) was a_German-born_American_actress of the_silent_era .
